Extracts data from lds.org using LDSTools APIs

Requires JRE verion 8 or higher
To execute:
java -jar lds-tools-export-1.0.jar ldsUsername ldsPassword path-to-export-file

example:
java -jar lds-tools-export-1.0.jar myUser myPass /temp/ward-export.csv

Note:
Don't use spaces in the file name or path.
